      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently faces significant mechanical challenges, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that requires immediate attention. The exterior has noticeable dents and rust, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts car.",
